content.rendered:
VABL Novice/Amateur Contest

Join us for an exciting showcase of rising boxing talents at the Victorian Amateur Boxing League (VABL) Novice/Amateur Contest. This event brings together novice and amateur fighters from across the state, battling it out in a series of thrilling bouts. Witness the determination, skill, and passion of the next generation of boxers as they compete under official rules, judged by certified professionals. Whether you’re a boxing enthusiast or new to the sport, this contest promises an action-packed experience with intense matchups and an electric atmosphere. Don’t miss your chance to see the future stars of boxing in action!
